OL,3,CSentence of care home rapist 'will not
OL,4,Cbe reviewed' after criticisms from MP
OL,6,FThe prison sentence of a care home
OL,7,Fworker who filmed himself raping
OL,8,Fresidents with dementia has been
OL,9,Fcondemned by an MP who is calling for
OL,10,Fa review.
OL,12,FJoshua Springer was jailed for 21
OL,13,Fyears last month for nine counts of
OL,14,Frape relating to four victims - three
OL,15,Fof whom had been under his care at a
OL,16,Fhome in Stamford, Lincolnshire.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
