OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1774966278
OL,3,CSentence of care home rapist 'will not
OL,4,Cbe reviewed' after criticisms from MP
OL,6,FLocal MP Alicia Kearns (Con) has
OL,7,Fcriticised the decision not to give
OL,8,FSpringer a life sentence, saying she
OL,9,Fis "deeply disappointed" to hear
OL,10,FAttorney General, Ellie Reeves, would
OL,11,Fnot be reviewing it.
OL,13,FAn application was made to re-examine
OL,14,FSpringer's jail time under the Unduly
OL,15,FLenient Sentence Scheme, however, a
OL,16,Fletter from Reeves' office said the
OL,17,Fdetails of the case did not meet the
OL,18,Fthreshold for the Court of Appeal.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
