OL,3,CSentence of care home rapist 'will not
OL,4,Cbe reviewed' after criticisms from MP
OL,6,FIn her letter, Ms Reeves said the bar
OL,7,Ffor increasing a sentence was "a very
OL,8,Fhigh one" and that courts only do so
OL,9,Fin "exceptional circumstances", such
OL,10,Fas cases where a judge has made "some
OL,11,Fgross error".
OL,13,F"In this case, the judge applied the
OL,14,Fappropriate guidelines, and after
OL,15,Fcareful consideration," wrote Ms
OL,16,FReeves. "I have concluded that this
OL,17,Fwas done correctly."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
