OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1774966278
OL,3,CSentence of care home rapist 'will not
OL,4,Cbe reviewed' after criticisms from MP
OL,6,FMs Kearns, MP for Rutland and
OL,7,FStamford, said Springer was a "vile
OL,8,Fpredator" who abused his position of
OL,9,Ftrust to "commit the most heinous
OL,10,Fcrimes against the most vulnerable".
OL,12,FShe said: "Whilst no sentence can undo
OL,13,Fthe horror he inflicted, committing
OL,14,Fnine rapes of the most vulnerable, and
OL,15,Fproducing indecent images of children,
OL,16,Fshould be a life sentence in my book."
OL,18,FSpringer, who is 36 and from Stamford,
OL,19,Fwas jailed in February at Lincoln
OL,20,FCrown Court after admitted nine
OL,21,Fcharges of rape.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
