OL,3,CSentence of care home rapist 'will not
OL,4,Cbe reviewed' after criticisms from MP
OL,6,FHe also admitted to making indecent
OL,7,Fimages of children and was given a
OL,8,FSexual Harm Prevention Order for the
OL,9,Frest of his life.
OL,11,FThe court heard he had been linked to
OL,12,Fone victim with DNA evidence, while
OL,13,Fhis mother reported him to the police
OL,14,Fcalling him a "rapist" and "borderline
OL,15,Fpaedo".
OL,17,FInvestigations into Springer also
OL,18,Funcovered 760 indecent images,
OL,19,Fincluding several showing babies being
OL,20,Fattacked.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
