OL,6,FThree of the victims had been
OL,7,Fresidents at the home, which cannot be
OL,8,Fnamed to protect their identities, and
OL,9,Fhad dementia. The fourth had been a
OL,10,Fwoman from an undisclosed location in
OL,11,FNorth Yorkshire.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
